                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-square-plus" style="font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(32,138,174); margin-top: 1rem;"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Plan Your Trips</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Create detailed itineraries with destinations, budgets, and notes for your perfect adventure.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style="height:40vh; width: 30vw; border-radius: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;">
