                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Explore Destinations</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Discover amazing trips planned by other travelers and get inspired for your next journey.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style="height: 40vh; width: 30vw; border-radius: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-users" style="font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(32,138,174); margin-top: 1rem;"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Share Experiences</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Connect with fellow travelers and share your favorite destinations and travel tips.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style=" height: 40vh; width: 30vw;  border-radius: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved" style="font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(32,138,174); margin-top: 1rem;"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Privacy Control</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Choose whether to keep your trips private or share them with the travel community.</p>
