                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style="height: 40vh; width: 30vw; border-radius: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-globe" style="font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(32,138,174); margin-top: 1rem;"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Global Community</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Join a worldwide community of travelers sharing experiences from every corner of the globe.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col">
                <div class="card" style=" height:40vh; width:30vw;  border-radius: 1rem; margin-left: 0.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-folder-tree" style="font-size: 3rem; color: rgb(32,138,174); margin-top: 1rem;"></i>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-center" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Smart Organization</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-center text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Keep all your travel plans organized in one place with our intuitive dashboard.</p>
