            <h1 style=" font-size: 3rem; color:white; font-weight: 00;">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h1>
            <p style=" width:60vw; color: white; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.4rem;margin-left: 17rem;">Join thousands of travelers who trust WanderPlan to organize their adventures. Create your account today and start planning your next unforgettable trip!</p>
            <div>
               <a class="btn btn-light" href="/user/signup" style=" margin-top:1.5rem; font-size:1.4rem;  width: 14rem; height: 3rem; color:rgb(32,138,174); margin-right: 1rem; border-radius: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;">Get Started Free</a> 
            </div>

    </div>
